review.reviewBody: Follows notes, makes orders quickly, always fresh, thanks!
Follow all instructions and food was so tasty..

The picture of the Side Pickles (8 slices) looks like they're deep fried.  I thought that's what I was getting.  What I got was 8 pickle slices like what you get on a Double Double Burger.  Not deep fried.  Disappointed as the rest of the meal was delisious.
